  "ai_usage": "Use for mobile-app marketing. Hero = phone mockup + store-badge links (labeled) + star rating (with text). Add alternating feature rows (image/text), a horizontal screenshot strip, and a download CTA band. Drop real screenshots into the phone/tiles, keep badges as accessible links, and respect reduced-motion for float/reveals. Recolor via --accent.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/app-landing.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Mobile App Landing</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"app-landing\",\n  \"title\": \"Mobile App Landing\",\n  \"summary\": \"A mobile-app landing: phone mock hero with App Store / Google Play badges and a rating, alternating feature rows, a screenshot strip, and a download CTA.\",\n  \"description\": \"A focused app marketing page — a hero pairing a phone mockup (with a live-looking app UI) and store-badge CTAs plus star rating, alternating image/text feature rows, a horizontal screenshot strip, and a final download band. Built to drive installs.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"landing\", \"app\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"mobile-app\", \"app-store\", \"download\", \"phone-mock\", \"ratings\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers.\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"CSS phone mock + reveals + a gentle float. No images (gradient screenshots). Light.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Store badges are labeled links; rating includes text; alternating rows keep logical order; focus-visible. Float/reveals respect reduced-motion.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--accent\", \"description\": \"Brand accent\", \"default\": \"#ff5c8a\" },\n    { \"name\": \"screens\", \"description\": \"Phone UI + screenshot tiles\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Single-platform (iOS only)\", \"QR code to install\", \"Pricing/IAP section\"],\n  \"related\": [\"clay-app\", \"link-in-bio\", \"spatial-depth\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for mobile-app marketing. Hero = phone mockup + store-badge links (labeled) + star rating (with text). Add alternating feature rows (image/text), a horizontal screenshot strip, and a download CTA band. Drop real screenshots into the phone/tiles, keep badges as accessible links, and respect reduced-motion for float/reveals. Recolor via --accent.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#0b0b14;--surface:#15151f;--line:#262635;--text:#f0eef8;--muted:#9a96b0;--accent:#ff5c8a;--accent2:#7c5cff;--r:18px;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:\"Inter\",system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:68px}\n  .brand{font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem}.brand .ic{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2))}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.4rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem}.links a:hover{color:var(--text)}\n  .hero{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:2.5rem;align-items:center;padding:2.5rem 0 4rem}\n  .rate{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem}.rate .s{color:#fbbf24}\n  h1{font-size:clamp(2.4rem,6vw,4rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:1.05;margin:.8rem 0 .6rem}\n  h1 .g{background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}\n  .hero p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.12rem;max-width:40ch;margin:0 0 1.4rem}\n  .badges{display:flex;gap:.7rem;flex-wrap:wrap}\n  .badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;background:#fff;color:#000;border-radius:12px;padding:.6rem 1rem;font-weight:700}\n  .badge small{display:block;font-size:.62rem;font-weight:600;opacity:.7}.badge .big{font-size:1rem;line-height:1}\n  .badge:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--accent);outline-offset:3px}\n  .phone-wrap{justify-self:center;position:relative}\n  .phone{width:260px;height:540px;border-radius:42px;background:#0a0a12;border:10px solid #222234;box-shadow:0 40px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.6);overflow:hidden;animation:float 6s ease-in-out infinite}\n  @keyframes float{50%{transform:translateY(-14px)}}\n  .scr{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#1b1530,#0a0a12);padding:1.2rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.8rem}\n  .scr .bar{height:6px;width:60px;background:#33334a;border-radius:3px;margin:0 auto .4rem}\n  .scr h4{margin:.2rem 0}.scr .row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border-radius:12px;padding:.6rem}\n  .scr .dot{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2))}\n  .scr .ln{height:8px;border-radius:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);flex:1}\n  .scr .cta{margin-top:auto;background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));text-align:center;border-radius:12px;padding:.7rem;font-weight:800}\n  section{padding:3.5rem 0}\n  .feat{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2.5rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:2.5rem}\n  .feat:nth-child(even) .ph{order:2}\n  .feat .ph{aspect-ratio:4/3;border-radius:var(--r);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent2),#22d3ee)}\n  .feat:nth-child(2) .ph{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),#ffb454)}\n  .feat h3{font-size:1.5rem;margin:0 0 .4rem}.feat p{color:var(--muted)}\n  .feat .ey{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.72rem}\n  .shots{display:flex;gap:1rem;overflow-x:auto;padding:1rem .2rem;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory}\n  .shots .s{flex:0 0 180px;height:380px;border-radius:24px;scroll-snap-align:center}\n  .ss1{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#7c5cff,#22d3ee)}.ss2{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#ff5c8a,#ffb454)}.ss3{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#34d399,#0ea5e9)}.ss4{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#a78bff,#ff6ec7)}\n  .download{text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,92,138,.15),rgba(124,92,255,.15));border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:24px;padding:3rem 1.5rem}\n  .download h2{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.6rem);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 1.2rem}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2.2rem 0;font-size:.9rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity .7s,transform .7s ease}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:820px){.hero,.feat{grid-template-columns:1fr}.feat:nth-child(even) .ph{order:0}.links{display:none}.badges{justify-content:center}.hero{text-align:center}.hero p{margin-inline:auto}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.phone{animation:none}.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav><div class=\"brand\"><span class=\"ic\"></span> Pulse</div><div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Features</a><a href=\"#\">Pricing</a><a href=\"#\">Support</a></div></nav>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"rate\"><span class=\"s\">★★★★★</span> 4.9 · 38k ratings <span style=\"position:absolute;left:-9999px\">rated 4.9 out of 5</span></div>\n        <h1>Your day, <span class=\"g\">in one tap</span>.</h1>\n        <p>Pulse keeps your habits, tasks, and focus in sync — beautifully, on every device.</p>\n        <div class=\"badges\">\n          <a class=\"badge\" href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Download on the App Store\"><span style=\"font-size:1.4rem\"></span><span></span><span><small>Download on the</small><span class=\"big\">App Store</span></span></a>\n          <a class=\"badge\" href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Get it on Google Play\"><span style=\"font-size:1.3rem\">▶</span><span><small>Get it on</small><span class=\"big\">Google Play</span></span></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"phone-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"phone\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"scr\">\n          <div class=\"bar\"></div><h4>Today</h4>\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"dot\"></span><span class=\"ln\"></span></div>\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"dot\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#22d3ee,#34d399)\"></span><span class=\"ln\"></span></div>\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"dot\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fbbf24,#ff5c8a)\"></span><span class=\"ln\"></span></div>\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"dot\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a78bff,#7c5cff)\"></span><span class=\"ln\"></span></div>\n          <div class=\"cta\">Start focus session</div>\n        </div></div>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n  </div>\n\n  <section class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"feat reveal\">\n      <div class=\"ph\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Feature preview\"></div>\n      <div><p class=\"ey\">Focus</p><h3>Deep work, on tap</h3><p>One button starts a distraction-free session and silences the noise across all your devices.</p></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"feat reveal\">\n      <div class=\"ph\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Feature preview\"></div>\n      <div><p class=\"ey\">Habits</p><h3>Streaks that stick</h3><p>Gentle reminders and satisfying progress keep your routines alive — without the guilt.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"shots\" aria-label=\"App screenshots\">\n      <div class=\"s ss1\"></div><div class=\"s ss2\"></div><div class=\"s ss3\"></div><div class=\"s ss4\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"download reveal\">\n    <h2>Get Pulse — free</h2>\n    <div class=\"badges\" style=\"justify-content:center\">\n      <a class=\"badge\" href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Download on the App Store\"><span><small>Download on the</small><span class=\"big\">App Store</span></span></a>\n      <a class=\"badge\" href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Get it on Google Play\"><span><small>Get it on</small><span class=\"big\">Google Play</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div></section>\n\n  <footer class=\"wrap\">© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Pulse · Available on iOS &amp; Android</footer>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.12});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
